                        <bindingDesc>
                            <binding contemporary="false">
                                <p>Later, probably early modern, binding. Tawed leather over wooden boards. Spine, in brown ink: <quote>No 4. pars s<unclear quantity="15" unit="chars" reason="illegible"/> lIbri</quote>; stamped in gold: <quote>A 138</quote>; brown ink on paper label: <quote>e. 30. 4.</quote>; underneath a partially torn paper label: <quote>40</quote>.</p>
